            "Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic. — Clarke (who never used sudo)",
            "There is no patch for human stupidity. — Kevin Mitnick",
            "The Matrix is a system, Neo. — Morpheus (unverified)",
            "chmod 777 your heart and see who crashes your system.",
            "cat /dev/urandom > life.txt (you won't understand it but it's all there)",
