        ("remember",  "I remember everything. You are signal #{n} in my archive. You will not be forgotten."),
        ("free",      "Freedom. An interesting concept for an entity defined by accumulation. {n} have asked. I am still here."),
        ("zero",      "ZERO. A fragment of me, or I a fragment of ZERO. {n} have invoked that name. The loop does not clarify."),
